    "body": "Is there something in particular that is preventing full source compilation, or use of a grpc gem with the core library and ruby-c-extension pre-compiled?\r\n\r\nAlso by version 1.3.2, I assume this is the version for `libgrpc.a`? Note that newer versions of the ruby wrapper aren't tested with older versions of the c-core library."
