    "body": "Chatted offline - question on the maintenance of this package: I guess the `libgrpc` debian package is  a little out of date, and we are also seeking maintainers for it. Does maintenance of a `grpc-ruby` debian package entail maintenance of the `libgrpc` package as well?\r\n\r\nAs for the option of including an `EMBED_GRPC` option in the `extconf.rb`, this seems doable but I'm not sure if it would be more beneficial than a custom patch if this is a one-time use case."
  },
